    title: 'Top 10 Wedding Cake Trends for 2026',
    metaTitle: 'Top 10 Wedding Cake Trends 2026 | San Diego Custom Cake Ideas | Auntie Lu\'s Bakery',
    metaDescription: 'Discover the top 10 wedding cake trends for 2026 from sculptural minimalism to geode designs. San Diego couples, get inspired for your big day with Auntie Lu\'s Bakery.',
    datePublished: '2026-03-05',
